### Heading 3
###### Heading 6

A paragraph with /italic/, *bold*, /*bold italic*/, _underline_, ~strike~,
=highlight=, {^super^}, {,sub,} and `inline code`. An escape: \*literal\*.
Smart typography: -- --- ... -> (c) (tm). Hard break at end:\

Links: [text](https://example.com), autolink <https://example.com>,
image ![alt](img.jpg), cross-ref </#heading-1>, reference [Page Name][],
and a footnote [^1] plus an inline note ^[right here].

A [span]{.fancy} and an :youtube[dQw4] extension. Social: @user and #tag.

